### ============================================
### Veo3 Internal API 测试文件
### 用途: 测试 Python Agent 调用的 Next.js 内部接口
### 使用: VS Code REST Client 插件
### ============================================

### 环境变量配置
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@internalApiKey = 1sgbP4oJbYjB4mItAd6zBCUY6EON3H+trpInY5oXbMg=
@testUserId = f54371bb-72c1-4c41-91ef-3c9c0b924704

### ============================================
### 1. 测试图像生成 API (关键帧)
### ============================================

### 1.1 提交图像生成任务 (Text-to-Image)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/image-generation
Authorization: Bearer {{internalApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{testUserId}}",
  "prompt": "A cute cat playing piano in a cozy living room, warm lighting, cinematic, high quality",
  "model": "nano-banana"
}

### 响应示例:
# {
#   "success": true,
#   "imageGenerationId": "abc-123-def",
#   "taskId": "kie_image_456",
#   "status": "PENDING"
# }

### 1.2 查询图像生成状态
# 将上面返回的 imageGenerationId 替换到下面
@imageGenerationId = e1a92d09-806f-47b8-a3d0-3c64b15b17b3

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/image-generation?id={{imageGenerationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{internalApiKey}}

### 响应示例:
# {
#   "success": true,
#   "id": "abc-123-def",
#   "status": "COMPLETED",  // PENDING, PROCESSING, COMPLETED, FAILED
#   "imageUrl": "https://r2.veo3ai.io/images/xxx.png",
#   "errorMessage": null
# }


### ============================================
### 2. 测试视频生成 API (Image-to-Video)
### ============================================

### 2.1 提交视频生成任务
# 使用上面生成的图像 URL
@keyframeUrl = https://r2.veo3ai.io/images/e1a92d09-806f-47b8-a3d0-3c64b15b17b3-1762263023898-0.png

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/video-generation
Authorization: Bearer {{internalApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{testUserId}}",
  "prompt": "A cute cat playing piano in a cozy living room, warm lighting, cinematic",
  "imageUrl": "{{keyframeUrl}}",
  "duration": 8,
  "model": "kie-veo3-image-to-video"
}

### 响应示例:
# {
#   "success": true,
#   "videoGenerationId": "def-456-ghi",
#   "taskId": "kie_video_789",
#   "status": "PENDING"
# }

### 2.2 查询视频生成状态
@videoGenerationId = 1311a860-f6a5-40f0-bb5b-48a44da033ee

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/video-generation?id={{videoGenerationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{internalApiKey}}

### 响应示例:
# {
#   "success": true,
#   "id": "def-456-ghi",
#   "status": "COMPLETED",  // PENDING, PROCESSING, COMPLETED, FAILED
#   "videoUrl": "https://r2.veo3ai.io/videos/xxx.mp4",
#   "errorMessage": null
# }


### ============================================
### 3. 测试积分扣除 API (可选)
### ============================================

### 3.1 扣除积分
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/credits/deduct
Authorization: Bearer {{internalApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{testUserId}}",
  "credits": 50.0,
  "transType": "agent_video_generation"
}

### 响应示例:
# {
#   "success": true,
#   "deducted": 10.0,
#   "remainingCredits": 490.0
# }


### ============================================
### 4. 错误测试
### ============================================

### 4.1 测试无效的 API Key
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/image-generation
Authorization: Bearer invalid-api-key
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{testUserId}}",
  "prompt": "Test prompt"
}

### 预期响应: 401 Unauthorized


### 4.2 测试不存在的模型
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/video-generation
Authorization: Bearer {{internalApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{testUserId}}",
  "prompt": "Test prompt",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/test.png",
  "model": "invalid-model-id"
}

### 预期响应: 500 Internal Server Error
# {"error": "Unknown model: invalid-model-id"}


### 4.3 测试缺少必填字段
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/video-generation
Authorization: Bearer {{internalApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{testUserId}}"
  // 缺少 prompt, imageUrl
}

### 预期响应: 400 Bad Request
# {"error": "Missing required fields: userId, prompt, imageUrl"}


### ============================================
### 5. 完整流程测试 (端到端)
### ============================================

### 步骤 1: 生成关键帧
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/image-generation
Authorization: Bearer {{internalApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{testUserId}}",
  "prompt": "A serene mountain landscape at sunset, vibrant colors, photorealistic",
  "model": "nano-banana"
}

# 记录返回的 imageGenerationId
# 然后轮询查询状态,直到 status = COMPLETED
# 获取 imageUrl


### 步骤 2: 等待关键帧完成后,生成视频
# 将上面获取的 imageUrl 填入下方
@finalImageUrl = https://r2.veo3ai.io/images/your-image-id.png

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/video-generation
Authorization: Bearer {{internalApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{testUserId}}",
  "prompt": "Camera slowly pans across the mountain landscape, golden hour lighting",
  "imageUrl": "{{finalImageUrl}}",
  "duration": 8,
  "model": "kie-veo3-image-to-video"
}

# 记录返回的 videoGenerationId
# 然后轮询查询状态,直到 status = COMPLETED
# 获取 videoUrl


### ============================================
### 使用说明
### ============================================

# 1. 安装 VS Code 插件: REST Client (humao.rest-client)
# 2. 确保 veo3-main/.env 中有 INTERNAL_API_KEY
# 3. 确保 veo3-main 服务运行在 localhost:3000
# 4. 点击每个请求上方的 "Send Request" 按钮执行
# 5. 查看响应结果

### 快速检查清单:
# [ ] veo3-main 服务运行中 (pnpm dev)
# [ ] INTERNAL_API_KEY 已配置
# [ ] 测试用户 ID 存在于数据库
# [ ] Kie.ai API Key 有效
# [ ] Supabase 连接正常

### 常见问题:
# - 401 Unauthorized → 检查 INTERNAL_API_KEY 是否正确
# - 500 Unknown model → 检查 model ID 是否在 config/video-models.ts 中
# - 500 其他错误 → 查看 veo3-main 控制台的详细错误日志
# - 超时 → 检查 Kie.ai API 是否正常响应

### 成功的标志:
# ✅ 图像生成: status 从 PENDING → PROCESSING → COMPLETED
# ✅ 视频生成: status 从 PENDING → PROCESSING → COMPLETED
# ✅ 最终获得 videoUrl: https://r2.veo3ai.io/videos/xxx.mp4
